      MESSAGE "Creation of request failed:" SKIP
              lcError
      VIEW-AS ALERT-BOX ERROR.
                          

   CLEAR FRAME rajat no-pause.
   liInvNum = 0.

   IF liCalled > 0 THEN LEAVE rajat.

END. /* rajat */

HIDE FRAME rajat no-pause.
